title: "Clinical Trial AI Evaluation — Methodology Notes"
abstract: >
  A methodology note from designing one high-fidelity adversarial evaluation
  case for AI systems performing cross-document clinical trial operations
  work. Documents the design approach, validation results, and three
  corrections caught during development. Contributed to the Raycaster
  Expert Network; the methodology is published, the eval content is not.
